MEC170x ECM Based I2C for SECO - Intel Amston Lake

%C [mec170 options] [generic options]

mec170 options:
-d bus_num          I2C bus number.(Default: 10)
-v                  Increase verbosity.(Default: 0)

Generic options for I2C resource manager libi2c-master:
--b bus_speed   Default bus speed. (Default: 100000)
--u unit        Unit number. Number to append to device name
                prefix (/dev/i2c). (Default: 0)

Following bus speeds are currently supported: 1MHZ, 100KHZ, 400KHZ.

Example:
%C -d10 --u1 --b100000
